DOMAIN,stream.binancefuture.com
DOMAIN,data.binance.com
DOMAIN,developers.binance.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,binance.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,binance.me
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,bnbdstatic.com

